 x4e h4 yefa ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">His previous promise. Deut. </div><div class="t m289 x4e h4 y1305 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">7:7, 8; 4:37, 38. </div><div class="t m2b6 x48 h4 y8c1 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m4cf x4e h4 y8c1 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God&apos;s people to be holy and </div><div class="t m6f3 x4e h4 y40a ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">peculiar. Ex. 19:5, 6. </div><div class="t m469 x15 h5 y4ed ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">II. God&apos;s Covenant Proclaimed </div><div class="t ma2 x73 h4 y706 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t m7e4 x4e h4 y15a0 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">A covenant between God and His </div><div class="t m2d8 x4e h4 y82a ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">people. Deut. 5:2-4. </div><div class="t m1cd x73 h4 ydc4 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. </div><div class="t mff x4e h4 yabc ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The covenant command, written by </div><div class="t m238 x4e h4 y788 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God&apos;s finger. Ex. 24:7; Deut. 4:13. </div><div class="t m1d0 x73 h4 y47b ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6. </div><div class="t m669 x4e h4 y7bd ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Israel broke the covenant they had </div><div class="t m15f x4e h4 y519 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">made. Ex. 32:7, 8. </div><div class="t ma3 xa5 h4 y598 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">7. A Saviour from sin needed. </div><div class="t ma4b x3d h4 y156e ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Heb. 9:8-12. </div><div class="t m404 x21 h5 ya47 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">III. Love and Obedience Desired </div><div class="t ma6e x9 h4 y524 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">8. Obedience to God&apos;s laws required. </div><div class="t mac4 x3d h4 y983 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Deut. 10:12, 13. </div><div class="t m143 x9 h4 y302 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">9. The commandments to be written </div><div class="t ma66 x3d h4 y545 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">in the heart. Ezek. 36:26; Heb. </div><div class="t mae7 x3d h4 yaf0 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">8:10. </div><div class="t m148 x7b h4 y4e9 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">10. Love to God and man the motive </div><div class="t m35f x3d h4 ye4 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">for obedience. Deut. 6:5 ; Lev. </div><div class="t m857 x3d h4 y17 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">19:18. </div><div class="t mbc x21 h5 y6d2 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">IV. Holiness Declared Essential • </div><div class="t m32e x7b h4 yaaf ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">11. Continual instruction in God&apos;s </div><div class="t m160 x3d h4 y6d4 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">requirements enjoined. Deut. </div><div class="t m711 x3d h4 y1939 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6:4-9. </div><div class="t m767 x7b h4 y52b ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">12. Holiness God&apos;s desire for His peo-</div><div class="t m88c x3d h4 ye8c ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ple. Deut. 26:16-19. </div><div class="t m287 x7b h4 yc83 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">13. Obedience one of the character-</div><div class="t m3ef xac h4 y1577 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">istics of those who will enter God&apos;s </div><div class="t m5f2 x3d h4 y9a5 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">kingdom. Isa. 1:19 ; 26:2. </div><div class="t m1e4 x2f h5 y7c1 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">THE LESSON </div><div class="t mf56 x12 h5 y463 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Introduction </div><div class="t mb4a x71 h4 y171d ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">It may seem strange to us that God </div><div class="t m6df x15 h4 y96c ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">should choose a specific nation in order </div><div class="t m172b x15 h4 ya24 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to reveal His will to mankind. But God </div><div class="t m3cb x15 h4 y447 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">had a definite purpose in view. &quot;He de-</div><div class="t mdd x15 h4 y2020 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">signed that the principles revealed through  </div><div class="t m5e1 x21 h4 y132c ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">His people should be the means of restoring </div><div class="t mb2 x70 h4 yfe7 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the moral image of God in man. </div><div class="t mfc x4b h4 ya9f ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;God&apos;s law must be exalted, His author-</div><div class="t m1ede x21 h4 y4a0 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ity maintained; and to the house of </div><div class="t m33e x21 h4 yfee ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Israel was given this great and noble work. </div><div class="t m480 x70 h4 y155e ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God separated them from the world, that </div><div class="t m7ed x21 h4 ybf4 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">He might commit to them a sacred trust. </div><div class="t ma9e x1f h6 y151d ff2 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">[ 10 ] </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
